    "body": "i took a look at code and don't see straightforward way to fix this, seems in renderer side there is some caching (https://github.com/electron/electron/blob/master/lib/renderer/api/remote.js#L236) and possibly interfering with ref counting in main process.   @tarruda can you please take a look, thanks."
